{"tid":194578,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無人理]前線統計員爆料：人口普查平板、制服流落民間　議員憂冒認洩資料","createTime":"2017-04-10T05:23:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T05:30:31.000Z","uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6f7a99b5dcc08bf847792394042b58006448a2e6","tid":194578,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/82679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F82679&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=9e3c8fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/82679</a><br />\n統計處去年進行中期人口普查時，遺失2部載有市民資料的平板電腦，事隔9個月始交代。有前線統計員向《香港01》爆料，指處方處理人口統計工具時相當粗疏，曾經載有市民私隱的國產平板電腦，事後竟然流落民間，轉贈安老院舍等機構；有離職的管理人員又私藏制服紀念。議員擔心一旦制服遺失，有人可能冒認統計處職員，借機套取市民資料。　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/82679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F82679&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNosQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=9e3c8fe6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/82679</a>"},{"pid":"00fcec2a08ecbb803a3bd8cd7eaa1638a8f8c883","tid":194578,"uid":40672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:24:16.000Z","msg":"全文自己入去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個人私隱嘢無人理"},{"pid":"83079debcf7771debbe0f61e4a257065b6676a12","tid":194578,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T05:30:31.000Z","msg":"平版電腦可抽出底版，搵專業公司於監察下物理銷毀底版。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}